Enum RuntimeEvent.EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RuntimeEvent.EventType>
      • goal.core.runtime.RuntimeEvent.EventType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RuntimeEvent.EventType>
    Enclosing class:
    RuntimeEvent

    public static enum RuntimeEvent.EventType
extends java.lang.Enum<RuntimeEvent.EventType>
    Event types that relate to platform related events which are NOT generated by an agent itself.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AGENT_BORN
      Event (type) generated when an agent has been (partially) created.
      AGENT_DIED
      Event (type) generated when an agent process has died.
      AGENT_IS_LOCAL_AND_READY
      Agent is running locally and ready to run.
      AGENT_REMOVED
      The agent was removed entirely from the system.
      ENVIRONMENT_KILLED
      The environment was killed
      ENVIRONMENT_LAUNCHED
      Event (type) generated when an environment has been launched by GOAL.
      ENVIRONMENT_RUNMODE_CHANGED
      Event (type) generated when the run mode of an environment has changed.
      MAS_BORN
      Event (type) generated when a MAS process has been started.
      MAS_DIED
      Event (type) generated when a MAS process has died.
      SCHEDULER_KILLED
      Event (type) generated when a GOAL scheduler has been killed.
      SCHEDULER_LAUNCHED
      Event (type) generated when a GOAL scheduler has been launched.
      SCHEDULER_SELECTED_AGENT
      Event (type) generated when a GOAL scheduler has selected AT LEAST one or possibly more agent(s) for execution.

      • MAS_BORN

        public static final RuntimeEvent.EventType MAS_BORN
        Event (type) generated when a MAS process has been started. Object is associated MASFileRegistry.

      • MAS_DIED

        public static final RuntimeEvent.EventType MAS_DIED
        Event (type) generated when a MAS process has died. Object is associated MASFileRegistry.

      • AGENT_BORN

        public static final RuntimeEvent.EventType AGENT_BORN
        Event (type) generated when an agent has been (partially) created. In case of messaging, this message is generated when the messagebox for the agent is created. Object is related Agent or a String with the agent name when agent is remote.

      • AGENT_REMOVED
